data.description: Get ready to tour this 3-bed, 2-bath home minutes from Bald Eagle State Park, Sayers Dam, and Russell P. Letterman Campground.  Appreciate fishing, boating, and camping with ease! Enjoy an open-concept floor plan and one-floor living with this bright and airy home with flow-through living space. A great place to call home just 20 miles to State College and 16 miles to Lock Haven. Sizable bedrooms include an owner's suite with owner's bath featuring a double vanity sink, whirlpool tub, and stand-up shower with ceramic tile flooring. The living area boasts newer hardwood flooring and a propane fireplace. Heat with efficiency with a wood-burning stove located in the basement. Last, there's plenty of storage space in the expansive basement and a convenient outdoor shed for landscaping needs. Bring the dream to life and schedule your tour today!
